content: Gyunam Park received the B.S. degree in business administration and computer science from UNIST (Ulsan National Institute of Science and Technology), Ulsan, South Korea, in 2017. He is currently a Master student in the Department of Industrial & Management Engineering at POSTECH (Pohang University of Science and Technology). His research interest includes process mining, data science, online operational support, machine learning, and deep learning.
